title: Starbucks on Town Center
headline: Spacious and Well Lit
description: A Starbucks with plenty of seating inside and out. It is a great workspace for coding or studying.
address: 1260 N Town Center Dr, Las Vegas, NV 89144

tables.quality: Wooden tables that are not fixed in place. Great for both groups and individuals.

chairs.quality: Most chairs are hard wood, mid-back, but there are soft cushioned benches along the front edge of the interior that give support for long work sessions.

ambience.quality: The large windows contribute to fantastic natural lighting. If you prefer to be outside, there is an outdoor area that have both shaded and non-shaded sections. The indoor lighting is comprised of bright but warm tones so there won't be any working in the dark.
